This juice is Amazing..so simple but so good.  I don't have TPA Bavarian Cream but I do have FW Bavarian Cream or FW Yogurt I used CAP Sweet Yogurt and I did the same percentages.  Even if you don't usually like Sweet Strawberry it works here, this is now my ADV as well.  I did use a bit more Super Sweet I like my juice SWEET, I used 1.5%  It was delicious on the Shake but the next morning it was twice as good.  I made 30 mils and it will be gone the day after I made it going to have to make a huge bottle tonight.  Love to all and Thanks Wayne of Diy or Die      &#xD;
&#xD;
UPDATE:  Vaped what I made then mixed a 120 ml 6mg and a 60ml 0mg for my Husband vaped through all that and just went through a panic because I wrote the name down wrong so when I went to look for it...couldn't find it...OMG...no panic like the panic of losing your current all day vape (pun intended).  I am now going to write keep the recipe in my Evernote ...can't let this happen again.
